    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>Why did I have to read this post on a Sunday morning when I am both in a rush and have no real bread to speak of? How can I eat my cereal with any semblance of pleasure now?</></>I&#8217;ll just have to plan ahead for next weekend so that I can make your dad&#8217;s recipe.</></>And of course, long live bisquick pancakes!</p>
