    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>I recently found your book at the library and completely enjoyed it &#8212; I had the wonderful opportunity to read a good portion of it with a sleeping baby in my arms all in one sitting yesterday. This morning I woke up and headed straight for the kitchen after dreaming of your French Toast recipe. And it went over so well. It was amazing. The whole family loved it. Thank you.</p>
