    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>Thanks to you Molly, and your dad for this great recipe. I just made it this morning and it was honestly the best french toast I have ever made. The oil really did make it crisp on the outside and puffy and custardy on the inside. I will never use another recipe again!</p>
